CBUILD RPM Lifecycle

  The CBUILD RPM lifecycle is a fascad on top of the standard autoconf lifecycle 
  adding maven dependency management and project management.  Patching is part
  of the lifecycle but probably seldom used.  The table below shows the different
  phases of the RPM Lifecycle and the goals (including standard maven goals)
  attached to them.

*------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| <<Phase>>              | <<Goals>> goals in beta release in <italics>                                                                |
*------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+ 
| validate               | {{{cbuild-plugin-parent/make-maven-plugin/validate-pom-mojo.html}validate-pom}}                             |
*------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+ 
| initialize             | {{{cbuild-plugin-parent/build-on-demand-maven-plugin/resolve-mojo.html}resolve dependencies}},              |
|                        | {{{cbuild-plugin-parent/patch-maven-plugin/resolve-patches-mojo.html}resolve patches}},                     |
|                        | {{{cbuild-plugin-parent/project-sources-maven-plugin/resolve-project-sources-mojo.html}resolve sources}},   |
|                        | {{{cbuild-plugin-parent/rpm-cbuild-maven-plugin/set-project-file-mojo.html}set project file}},              |
|                        | {{{cbuild-plugin-parent/multibuild-optimizer-maven-plugin/check-package-staleness-mojo.html}chk pkg stale}} |
*------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+ 
| generate-sources       |                                                                                                             |
*------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+ 
| process-sources        | {{{cbuild-plugin-parent/patch-maven-plugin/apply-directory-mojo.html}apply directory}}                      |
*------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+ 
